CONDITION: The consent for the following details below is hereby granted for the benefit of occupation of the premises for the applicant's son Archie Campbell and shall be reinstated to the satisfaction of the Local Planning Authority within 6 months of this occupation ceasing.

i)	installation of lift running from ground floor to basement levels and all associated works;
ii)	creation of opening on floor and associated removal of fabric between ground floor and basement;
iii)	installation of boxing in chimney breast alcove.

REASON: To protect the special interest of the building included on the statutory list whilst recognising the special circumstances surrounding the proposal and the specific needs of the applicant's son, Archie Campbell.
